data.description: Don't miss this spacious four bedroom two and one half bath 2-story home in the popular Olympia Estates subdivision in Missouri City! With over 2700 square feet of living space, this home is perfect for any type of lifestyle. Approach the brick-faced home and enter through a custom hardwood door and into a vaulted and tiled entry foyer. Move into a spacious and sun filled living area with a two-log fireplace and ample room for your furnishings. The adjacent kitchen features a granite countertop and more than adequate storage and features a walk-in pantry. It also includes a large eat-in kitchen area. The downstairs master is a very spacious 19 x 18 square feet and includes a large closet and ensuite bath including a separate bathing tub and shower as well as large vanities. The large upstairs area includes a game/play area and three additional bedrooms all spacious in size. The home also includes a two car garage and an oversized, fenced back yard for your outdoor enjoyment.
